quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  37,22,(Kudzanenedwa kuti); “Bweretsani anthu ochimwa pamodzi ndi anzawo ndi zinthu zimene iwo anali kupembedza.”
  37,23,“Kuonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni ndipo atsogolereni ku njira ya kumoto.”
  37,24,"“Ndipo aimitseni. Ndithudi, iwo ayenera kufunsidwa.”"
  37,25,“Kodi mwatani? Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani inu simuli kuthandizana?”
  37,26,Iyayi! Koma iwo lero ndi odzipereka
  37,27,Ndipo iwo adzafunsana wina ndi mnzake
  37,28,"Iwo adzati, “Ndinu amene munali kubwera kwa ife kuchokera kudzanja lamanja.”"
  37,29,"Iwo adzayankha kuti, “Iyayi, Inuyo simunali okhulupirira.”"
  37,30,“Ndipo ife tidalibe ulamuliro pa inu. Iyayi! Inu mudali osamva.”
  37,31,“Kotero chiweruzo cha Ambuye wathu chadza pa ife. Ndithudi tsopano tidzachilawa.”
  37,32,“Choncho ife tidakusocheretsani chifukwa nafenso tidali osochera.”
  37,33,"Ndipo, ndithudi, patsiku limeneli onse adzalandirana chilango pakati pa wina ndi mnzake"
  37,34,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timachitira ndi anthu olakwa
  37,35,"Ndithudi pamene iwo, adauzidwa kuti, “Kulibe mulungu wina koma Mulungu weniweni, iwo anali kudzitukumula.”"
  37,36,"Ndipo adanena kuti, “Kodi ife tisiye milungu yathu chifukwa cha Mlakatuli wamisala?”"
  37,37,Iyayi. Iye wadza ndi choonadi ndipo ali kutsimikizira uthenga wa Atumwi amene adadza kale
  37,38,"Ndithudi, inu mudzalangidwa kwambiri"
  37,39,Ndipo inu mudzalandira mphotho molingana ndi ntchito zanu
  37,40,Kupatula akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu
  37,41,Kwa iwo mphotho yawo ndi yodziwika
  37,42,Zipatso ndipo iwo adzalemekezeka kwambiri
  37,43,M’minda ya chisangalalo
  37,44,Atakhala pa mipando ya chifumu moyang’anizana
  37,45,Pakati pawo padzaperekedwa chikho cha vinyo wabwino
  37,46,oyera ndiponso okoma kwa iwo amene amamwa
  37,47,Simudzakhala mavuto mu icho ndipo sichidzawatopetsa
  37,48,Ndipo pakati pawo padzakhala akazi angwiro opanda chimasomaso
  37,49,Okhala ngati mazira osamalidwa bwino
  37,50,Ndipo adzadza kwa anzawo ndi kumafunsana wina ndi mnzake
  37,51,"Wina wochokera pakati pawo adzayankhula nati, “Ndithudi ine ndinali ndi bwenzi langa.”"
  37,52,“Amene amakonda kunena kuti; “Kodi ndiwe mmodzi mwa okhulupirira?”
  37,53,"“Kodi ife tikafa ndi kusanduka dothi ndi mafupa, tidzatengedwa kupita ku chiweruzo"
  37,54,"Iye adati, “Kodi iwe ungaone pansi?”"
  37,55,Motero adayang’ana pansi ndipo adamuona iye ali pakati pa moto wa ku Gahena
  37,56,"Iye adati, “Pali Mulungu! Iwe udatsala pang’ono kundipweteka.”"
  37,57,"“Ndipo kukadapanda chisomo cha Ambuye wanga ine, ndithudi, ndikadakhala mmodzi wa iwo.”"
  37,58,“Kodi ndiye kuti ife sitidzafa?”
  37,59,"“Kupatula kufa koyamba, kodi ife sitidzalangidwa?”"
  37,60,Ndithudi uku ndiko kupambana kwenikweni
  37,61,"Pofuna kupeza zotere, alekereni alimbikire amene akufuna kuti alimbikirewo"
  37,62,Kodi chimenechi ndi chabwino kapena mtengo wa Zaqqum
  37,63,Ndithudi tazipanga izi kukhala mayesero kwa anthu olakwa
  37,64,Ndithudi umenewu ndi mtengo umene umamera pansi pa Gahena
  37,65,Zipatso zake zili ngati mitu ya a Satana
  37,66,Ndithudi iwo adzadya zimenezi ndi kukhutitsa mimba zawo ndi zipatsozo
  37,67,"Ndithudi iwo akadzadya, adzamwa chakumwa chokonzedwa ndi madzi owira"
  37,68,Ndithudi iwo adzapita ku Gahena
  37,69,Ndithudi iwo adapeza makolo awo ali osochera
  37,70,Kotero iwo ali kutsatira mapazi awo
  37,71,Ndithudi makolo awo adasochera iwo asanadze
  37,72,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ife tidatumiza Atumwi pakati pawo"
  37,73,Ndipo taona zimene zidadza kwa iwo amene adachenjezedwa
  37,74,Kupatula akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu omwe ndi anthu olungama